window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Don't make an enemy of the mob.</p> <p>Still recuperating after being shot, Alexander Fairhaven has a new challenge to deal with - his brother's gambling addiction.</p> <p>As Alexander and Elizabeth settle into their new lives together, the shadows of Nick's problems linger.</p> <p>Will Nick find a way to escape his demons? Or will New Year's bring an end to Alexander and Elizabeth's happiness?</p>"; 
